methods.name: public Builder setSatelliteId(@IntRange(from = 0) int satId)
methods.comment: Sets the satellite ID defined in the ICD of the given constellation.

methods.name: public Builder setCarrierFrequencyHz(@FloatRange(from = 0.0f, fromInclusive = false) float carrierFrequencyHz)
methods.comment: Sets the carrier frequency in Hz.

methods.name: public Builder setProbabilityLineOfSight(@FloatRange(from = 0.0f, to = 1.0f) float probSatIsLos)
methods.comment:
* Sets the line-of-sight probability of the satellite at the given location in the range
         * between 0 and 1.

methods.name: public Builder clearProbabilityLineOfSight()
methods.comment:
* Clears the line-of-sight probability of the satellite at the given location. * *

This is to negate {@link #setProbabilityLineOfSight} call.

methods.name: public Builder setExcessPathLengthMeters(@FloatRange(from = 0.0f) float combinedExcessPathLengthMeters)
methods.comment:
* Sets the combined excess path length to be subtracted from pseudorange before using it in
         * calculating location.

methods.name: public Builder clearExcessPathLengthMeters()
methods.comment:
* Clears the combined excess path length. * *

This is to negate {@link #setExcessPathLengthMeters} call.

methods.name: public Builder setExcessPathLengthUncertaintyMeters(@FloatRange(from = 0.0f) float combinedExcessPathLengthUncertaintyMeters)
methods.comment: Sets the error estimate (1-sigma) for the combined excess path length estimate.

methods.name: public Builder clearExcessPathLengthUncertaintyMeters()
methods.comment:
* Clears the error estimate (1-sigma) for the combined excess path length estimate. * *

This is to negate {@link #setExcessPathLengthUncertaintyMeters} call.

methods.name: public Builder setCombinedAttenuationDb(@FloatRange(from = 0.0f) float combinedAttenuationDb)
methods.comment: * Sets the combined attenuation in Db.

methods.name: public Builder clearCombinedAttenuationDb()
methods.comment:
* Clears the combined attenuation. * *

This is to negate {@link #setCombinedAttenuationDb} call.

methods.name: public Builder setReflectingPlane(@Nullable GnssReflectingPlane reflectingPlane)
methods.comment:
* Sets the reflecting plane information.
         *
         * @deprecated Combined excess path does not have a reflecting plane.

methods.name: public GnssSingleSatCorrection build()
methods.comment: Builds a {@link GnssSingleSatCorrection} instance as specified by this builder.
